{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"9242","heading":"Report on North Korean prison camps","label":"9242 Report on North Korean prison camps","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/ch99/schIII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the camp’s estimated prisoner population;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the camp’s geographical coordinates;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the reasons for the confinement of the prisoners;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the camp’s primary industries and products, and the end users of any goods produced in the camp;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the individuals and agencies responsible for conditions in the camp;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the conditions under which prisoners are confined, with respect to the adequacy of food, shelter, medical care, working conditions, and reports of ill-treatment of prisoners; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"7","heading":null,"label":"7","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a/7","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fa%2F7","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"imagery, to include satellite imagery of the camp, in a format that, if published, would not compromise the sources and methods used by the United States intelligence community to capture geospatial imagery.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Form","label":"b Form","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9242","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9242%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The report required under subsection (a) may be included in the first human rights report required to be submitted to Congress after , under sections 2151n(d) and 2304(b) of this title.February 18, 2016","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
